<p>训练流程</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="20"><img src="https://tcs-ga.teambition.net/storage/111x083e68915bf75144fc94674313842ec3?Signature=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJBcHBJRCI6IjU5Mzc3MGZmODM5NjMyMDAyZTAzNThmMSIsIl9hcHBJZCI6IjU5Mzc3MGZmODM5NjMyMDAyZTAzNThmMSIsIl9vcmdhbml6YXRpb25JZCI6IiIsImV4cCI6MTU5OTc4NTQyNywiaWF0IjoxNTk5MTgwNjI3LCJyZXNvdXJjZSI6Ii9zdG9yYWdlLzExMXgwODNlNjg5MTViZjc1MTQ0ZmM5NDY3NDMxMzg0MmVjMyJ9.cb1P6q2qtQVCvmDxbYO1gAjFOGHRHVrEz23VBrLEKOA&amp;download=image.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
